Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.56,0:20:00.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害你这么痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.20,0:20:06.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.84,0:20:12.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是  我是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.71,0:20:18.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是Rebecca
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.66,0:21:02.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把Rebeccaさん那样放着真的好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.96,0:21:06.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她还要那样过1500年真的好可怜喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.20,0:21:10.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘记怨恨是需要时间的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.74,0:21:13.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要很长很长的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.71,0:21:14.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.97,0:21:19.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过  反正是睡着的 1500年转眼间就过去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.51,0:21:22.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如我们来祈祷当Rebeccaさん醒来的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.92,0:21:27.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界会比现在变得更美好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.95,0:21:29.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得是呢

